<p>這篇文章會以逐步教學為主，會比較詳細也比較繁雜</p>
<p>如果需要以提示為主的說明可以看柯基發的文 (&nbsp;<a href="../1129359603876068/2017/04/05/CPE%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82%E7%A8%8B%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8(%E5%90%AB%E7%B7%A8%E8%AD%AF%E5%99%A8).html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">這裡</a>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<a href="http://pws.niu.edu.tw/~b0543016/CPE.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">這裡</a>&nbsp;)</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>一、目錄</h2>
<h3>A. 前置作業</h3>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">1. 安裝 .Net Framework</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">2. 安裝編譯器MinGW</p>
<h3>B. 安裝主程式</h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>二、正文</h2>
<h3>A. 前置作業</h3>
<h4>安裝 .Net Framework</h4>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step1.</span></strong>&nbsp;前往微軟的下載頁面 <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/zh-tw/download/details.aspx?id=1639" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.microsoft.com/zh-tw/download/details.aspx?id=1639</a></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step2.</span></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;點擊下載按鈕</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step3.</span></strong>&nbsp;依照作業系統選擇要下載的檔案</p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step4.</span></strong>&nbsp;下載檔案後執行並且安裝</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4>安裝編譯器MinGW</h4>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step1.</span></strong>&nbsp;前往MinGW官網下載MinGW的Installer</p>
<p>網址 : <a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw/</a></p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step2.</span></strong>&nbsp;開啟下載完的Installer，按照預設的設定，Continue一路按到底 (?</p>
<p>特別注意的是為了讓瘋狂程設判定，MinGW的安裝路徑必須在C槽下，也就是說安裝時路徑也是按照預設，不要更動。</p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step3.</span></strong>&nbsp;一切安裝完畢後應該會開啟「MinGW Installation Manager」，這裡要將mingw32-gcc-g++標註為Mark for&nbsp;Installation</p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step4.</span></strong>&nbsp;勾選之後就可以選擇Installation &rarr; Apply Changes 安裝了</p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step5.</span></strong>&nbsp;按下Apply就可以開始安裝、下載</p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>
<h3>B. 安裝主程式</h3>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step1.</span></strong>&nbsp;進入瘋狂程設官網</p>
<p>網址 : <a href="http://coding-frenzy.arping.me/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">http://coding-frenzy.arping.me/</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step2.</span></strong>&nbsp;進入瘋狂程設官網</p>
<p>點選「安裝專用軟體」</p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step3.</span></strong>&nbsp;找到最新版瘋狂程設軟體並下載</p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step4.</span></strong>&nbsp;將下載下來的壓縮檔解壓縮到硬碟根目錄下 (例如C:\CodingFrenzy 或是 D:\CodingFrenzy)</p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step5.</span></strong>&nbsp;解壓縮後執行&nbsp;CodingFrenzy.exe</p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Step6.</span></strong>&nbsp;之後要開啟瘋狂程設都是執行&nbsp;CodingFrenzy.exe ，因此可以建立捷徑方便使用</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>安裝大致如此，至於使用的話可以不必申請帳號，直接以訪客登入即可。</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
